reviewText: Just the thing I wanted. In great condition. I couldn't ask for better service. I was very pleased with everything.

Very happy with the purchase and these are used.  I'm very pleased so far with my 'used' DVD/CD buys on Amazon.  I've watched 3 of them so far and didn't fall asleep once! :)  I enjoy learning our countries history, again..in this way.  They seem to be historically correct and they are well done production wise.
A FANTASTIC collection of some of the best History channel programing.  I can't wait to buy the 2007 collection!
